<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Selectors and Properties</title>
    <style>
    /* Apply background color and curved corners */
body {
    background-color: #a8d0e6; 
    color: black;               
    padding: 20px;              
    margin: 20px;               
    border-radius: 25px;        
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);}
      

        /* Element Selector */
        p {
            color: brown;
            font-size: 19px;
        }

        /* Class Selector */
        .highlight {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* ID Selector */
        #unique-element {
            color: purple;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        /* Attribute Selector */
        [title] {
            color: green;
        }

        /* Pseudo-Class */
        a:hover {
            color: purple;
        }

        /* Pseudo-Element */
        p::first-letter {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: pink;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>CSS Selectors</h1>
    <p>This is a paragraph which is just a normal paragraph looking paragraph so read it like a paragraph cause why not cause it is a paragraph.This is a paragraph which is just a normal paragraph looking paragraph so read it like a paragraph cause why not cause it is a paragraph.This is a paragraph which is just a normal paragraph looking paragraph so read it like a paragraph cause why not cause it is a paragraph.This is a paragraph which is just a normal paragraph looking paragraph so read it like a paragraph cause why not cause it is a paragraph.This is a paragraph which is just a normal paragraph looking paragraph so read it like a paragraph cause why not cause it is a paragraph.</p>
    <p class="highlight">This paragraph needs to get highlighted so I'm highlighting it. But prefer to treat it like a normal paragraph cause ofcourse it is only a prargraph.</p>
    <p id="unique-element">This has to be a unique element.So, sir treat it as a unique element. </p>
